OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers to strike in
OL,4,Cthe New Year
OL,6,FBirmingham bin workers are to strike
OL,7,Fin the New Year in a dispute over pay.
OL,9,FThe Unite Union has announced the
OL,10,Fcity's bin workers will undertake
OL,11,F'extensive action' from January 2nd
OL,12,F2025 - with strikes due to take place
OL,13,Ffrom 6th January.
OL,15,FThe dispute will involve more than 350
OL,16,Fmembers of Unite.
