OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers to strike in
OL,4,Cthe New Year
OL,6,FAccording to the Union, it is a result
OL,7,Fof the city council's decision to
OL,8,Fabolish the 'safety-critical' Waste
OL,9,FRecycling and Collection Officer
OL,10,F(WRCO) role.
OL,12,FThe Union claims 150 affected workers,
OL,13,Fmany of whom have worked for decades
OL,14,Ffor the council, face losing #8,000 a
OL,15,Fyear, and cuts could also reduce
OL,16,Ffuture pension payments.
