OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers to strike in
OL,4,Cthe New Year
OL,6,FUnite General Secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "Unite is not prepared to see
OL,8,Fits workers face a huge pay cut, nor
OL,9,Fwill it allow the council to
OL,10,Frecklessly cut safety-critical roles
OL,11,Fwhich risks the safety of workers and
OL,12,Fthe general public.
OL,14,F"Unite is totally focussed on
OL,15,Fprotecting the pay and safety of its
OL,16,Fmembers and will leave no stone
OL,17,Funturned in resolving this dispute."
