OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers to strike in
OL,4,Cthe New Year
OL,6,FFrom 2nd January, the Union said an
OL,7,Fovertime ban will be in place as well
OL,8,Fas a work-to-rule, which will mean
OL,9,Fworkers adhering to official start and
OL,10,Ffinish times and returning to the work
OL,11,Fyard for their 15-minute break and 30-
OL,12,Fminute lunch period. The Union said:
OL,13,F"This will cause considerable
OL,14,Fdisruption."
OL,16,FIn addition, there will be 12 days of
OL,17,Ffull strike action, with the first
OL,18,Fstrike on 6th January.
