OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers to strike in
OL,4,Cthe New Year
OL,6,FUnite regional officer Zoe Mayou said:
OL,7,F"Unite has bent over backwards to
OL,8,Fresolve this dispute but the council
OL,9,Fhas negotiated in bad faith and is
OL,10,Fsimply refusing to treat its workers
OL,11,Fwith fairness and decency.
OL,13,F"The strikes, overtime ban and work to
OL,14,Frule will cause huge disruption to
OL,15,Frefuse services throughout Birmingham
OL,16,Fbut this dispute is entirely of the
OL,17,Fcouncil's own making. The solution to
OL,18,Fthis dispute is in the council's
OL,19,Fhands."
