OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers to strike in
OL,4,Cthe New Year
OL,6,FIn response, a Birmingham City Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We are
OL,8,Fdisappointed that this action is
OL,9,Ftaking place, but we are continuing to
OL,10,Fwork through the dispute resolution
OL,11,Fprocedure. We would like to assure
OL,12,Fresidents that we will do all we can
OL,13,Fto minimise disruption during any
OL,14,Fpotential industrial action.
