OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers to strike in
OL,4,Cthe New Year
OL,6,F"We thank residents for their
OL,7,Funderstanding and patience during this
OL,8,Fchallenging period and assure everyone
OL,9,Fthat we are committed to resolving the
OL,10,Fsituation in the best interest of all
OL,11,Fparties involved. Up-to-date
OL,12,Finformation will be provided via our
OL,13,Fwebsite, social media and encourage
OL,14,Fresidents to sign up to bin collection
OL,15,Fnewsletter.
