OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers to strike in
OL,4,Cthe New Year
OL,6,F"Ensuring the safety of our employees
OL,7,Fand residents is taken extremely
OL,8,Fseriously, and health and safety is
OL,9,Feveryone's responsibility. We have
OL,10,Fundertaken steps to ensure Birmingham
OL,11,FCity Council colleagues affected by
OL,12,Fthe change in working arrangements are
OL,13,Fsupported. There are several options
OL,14,Fthat are available to suit different
OL,15,Fpersonal circumstances, and of the 170
OL,16,Faffected employees, over 130 have
OL,17,Falready opted for redeployment, driver
OL,18,Ftraining or voluntary redundancy.
