OL,6,F"We have moved quickly to minimise
OL,7,Fthis period of uncertainty for
OL,8,Feveryone. We are committed to working
OL,9,Fwith our colleagues across the service
OL,10,Ffor the best outcome so that we
OL,11,Fdeliver a consistent and reliable
OL,12,Fservice that Birmingham residents
OL,13,Fdeserve."
